<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>옥내 누수사용료 적용 신청서</title>
<style>
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', '맑은 고딕', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
  font-size: 10pt;
  background: #d0d0d0;
  color: #000;
}

.control-panel {
  position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
  z-index: 9999; flex-wrap: wrap; font-size: 9.5pt;
}
.panel-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 10pt; margin-right: 8px; white-space: nowrap; }
.ctrl-sep { width: 1px; height: 24px; background: #555; }
.ctrl-btn {
  background: #333; color: #fff; border: 1px solid #666;
  padding: 5px 14px; cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 9pt; border-radius: 3px; white-space: nowrap;
}
.ctrl-btn:hover { background: #555; }
.ctrl-btn.active { background: #2a7ae2; border-color: #2a7ae2; }
.ctrl-label { font-size: 8.5pt; color: #aaa; white-space: nowrap; }

.pages-wrap { padding: 60px 0 40px; }

.page {
  width: 210mm;
  padding: 14mm 20mm 12mm;
  margin: 0 auto 14px;
  background: #fff;
}

.doc-title {
  font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 900;
  text-align: center; letter-spacing: 2px;
  margin-bottom: 10px; padding-bottom: 8px;
  border-bottom: 2.5px solid #000;
}

.form-block {
  border: 1.5px solid #000;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  display: flex;
}

.section-tag {
  width: 26px; min-width: 26px;
  background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 8pt; font-weight: 700;
  writing-mode: vertical-rl; letter-spacing: 4px;
  padding: 6px 0;
}

.block-inner { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

.f-row {
  display: flex; flex: 1;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #bbb;
}
.f-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.f-row-tall { display: flex; flex: 2; }

/* ── 레이블: 고정너비 + justify-content:space-between ── */
.field-label {
  width: 76px; min-width: 76px;
  background: #f0f0f0;
  border-right: 1px solid #bbb;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 3px 6px;
  font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.4; text-align: center;
}

.f-val {
  flex: 1; padding: 5px 7px;
  font-size: 9pt; display: flex; align-items: center;
}
.f-val-tall {
  flex: 1; padding: 5px 7px; font-size: 9pt;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
}

.fi {
  border: none; outline: none; font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 9pt; width: 100%; background: transparent; color: #000;
}
.fi:focus { background: #fffde7; }
.fi-tall {
  resize: none; width: 100%; height: auto; min-height: 0;
  line-height: 1.5; border: none; outline: none;
  font-family: inherit; font-size: 9pt; background: transparent;
}
.fi-tall:focus { background: #fffde7; }
.fi-sync { color: #1a5fa8; }

.body-text {
  font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 1.85;
  margin: 8px 2px 10px; padding: 7px 12px;
  border-left: 3px solid #1a1a1a; background: #fafafa;
}

.sign-date { text-align: center; font-size: 10pt; margin: 8px 0 5px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
.sign-input-row {
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 2.2; gap: 4px;
}
.sign-input-row .fi-inline {
  border: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;
  outline: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 9.5pt;
  width: 80px; text-align: center; background: transparent;
}
.sign-input-row .fi-inline:focus { background: #fffde7; }
.sign-line { text-align: center; font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 2.2; }
.recipient-line { font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin: 7px 0; }
.attach-text { font-size: 9pt; line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 4px; color: #333; }

.cut-wrap { margin: 14px 0 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
.cut-line { flex: 1; border: none; border-top: 1.5px dashed #777; }
.cut-label { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #888; white-space: nowrap; }
.receipt-title { font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 900; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.receipt-row { font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 2.0; }
.receipt-confirm { font-size: 9.5pt; margin: 8px 0 4px; }
.receipt-sign { text-align: right; font-size: 9.5pt; line-height: 2.1; }
.note-box {
  margin-top: 8px; padding: 6px 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc; background: #f8f8f8;
  font-size: 8pt; line-height: 1.9; color: #444;
}

/* ── PAGE 2 ── */
.page-title {
  font-size: 13.5pt; font-weight: 900;
  text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px;
  padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2.5px solid #000;
}

.field-rows {
  border: 1.5px solid #000; margin-bottom: 8px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.fr {
  display: flex; flex: 1;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #bbb; min-height: 32px;
}
.fr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

/* 수리확인서 레이블: 글자들을 space-between으로 균등 배분 */
.fl {
  width: 120px; min-width: 120px;
  background: #f0f0f0; border-right: 1px solid #bbb;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700;
  /* 글자 균등 배분 핵심 */
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

/* · 기호는 왼쪽 고정, 나머지 글자들만 space-between */
.fl-inner {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-left: 4px;
}

.fv {
  flex: 1; padding: 5px 8px; font-size: 9pt;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
}

.note-small { font-size: 7.5pt; color: #555; margin: 4px 0 7px 2px; line-height: 1.6; }

/* 업체 박스 */
.company-box {
  border: 1.5px solid #000; margin-bottom: 10px;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
}
.cr { display: flex; flex: 1; border-bottom: 1px solid #bbb; min-height: 30px; }
.cr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

/* 업체 레이블: 동일하게 space-between, 가운데 정렬 */
.cl {
  width: 120px; min-width: 120px;
  background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; border-right: 1px solid #555;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700;
  display: flex; align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.cv {
  flex: 1; padding: 5px 8px; font-size: 9pt;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
}

.photo-note {
  font-size: 9.5pt; font-weight: 700; padding: 6px 2px;
  border-top: 1.5px solid #000; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #000; margin: 8px 0;
}
.confirm-footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 2.2; }

/* 사진대장 */
.photo-page-title {
  font-size: 15pt; font-weight: 900; text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 14px; padding-bottom: 8px;
  border-bottom: 2.5px solid #000; letter-spacing: 2px;
}
.photo-header {
  background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff;
  font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; padding: 6px 0;
}
.photo-card { border: 1.5px solid #222; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.photo-area {
  flex: 1; background: #f5f5f5; border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 0;
}
.photo-placeholder { color: #ccc; font-size: 8.5pt; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; }
.photo-upload-area {
  width: 100%; height: 100%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer; position: relative;
}
.photo-upload-area img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; }
.photo-upload-area input[type=file] { position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0; cursor: pointer; z-index: 2; }

.photo-page-4 {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  height: 297mm; padding: 14mm 20mm 12mm;
  background: #fff; margin: 0 auto 14px; width: 210mm;
}
.photo-grid-4 { flex: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; min-height: 0; }
.photo-page-2 {
  display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  height: 297mm; padding: 14mm 20mm 12mm;
  background: #fff; margin: 0 auto 14px; width: 210mm;
}
.photo-grid-2 { flex: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; min-height: 0; }

@media print {
  body { background: #fff; }
  .control-panel { display: none !important; }
  .pages-wrap { padding: 0; }
  .page, .photo-page-4, .photo-page-2 { margin: 0; page-break-after: always; }
  .fi-sync { color: #000; }
  @page { size: A4; margin: 0; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="control-panel">
  <span class="panel-title">📋 찰떡누수 신청서</span>
  <div class="ctrl-sep"></div>
  <span class="ctrl-label">사진대장 출력:</span>
  <button class="ctrl-btn active" id="btn-4" onclick="setPhotoMode('4')">4장 (1페이지)</button>
  <button class="ctrl-btn" id="btn-2" onclick="setPhotoMode('2')">2장씩 (2페이지)</button>
  <div class="ctrl-sep"></div>
  <button class="ctrl-btn" onclick="window.print()" style="background:#2a7ae2;border-color:#2a7ae2;">🖨 인쇄 / PDF 저장</button>
</div>

<div class="pages-wrap">

<!-- ═══ PAGE 1 ═══ -->
<div class="page">
  <div class="doc-title">옥내 누수사용료 적용 신청서</div>

  <div class="form-block" style="min-height:62px;">
    <div class="section-tag">수&nbsp;용&nbsp;가</div>
    <div class="block-inner">
      <div class="f-row">
        <div class="field-label">주&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;소</div>
        <div class="f-val"><input class="fi" id="addr" oninput="sync()" placeholder="주소를 입력하세요"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="f-row">
        <div class="field-label">수용가번호</div>
        <div class="f-val" style="border-right:1px solid #bbb;">
          <input class="fi" id="custno" oninput="sync()" placeholder="수용가번호">
        </div>
        <div class="field-label">연&nbsp;락&nbsp;처</div>
        <div class="f-val"><input class="fi" id="tel" oninput="sync()" placeholder="연락처"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-block" style="min-height:90px;">
    <div class="section-tag">신&nbsp;고&nbsp;내&nbsp;용</div>
    <div class="block-inner">
      <div class="f-row">
        <div class="field-label">누 수 일 시</div>
        <div class="f-val" style="border-right:1px solid #bbb;">
          <input class="fi" id="leak_date" oninput="sync()" placeholder="누수 발생 일시">
        </div>
        <div class="field-label" style="line-height:1.3;">누&nbsp;수<br>수리일자</div>
        <div class="f-val"><input class="fi" id="repair_date" oninput="sync()" placeholder="수리 완료일"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="f-row-tall">
        <div class="field-label" style="line-height:1.3;">누수위치 및<br>발생사유</div>
        <div class="f-val-tall">
          <textarea class="fi-tall" id="leak_loc" style="height:auto; min-height:0;" oninput="sync()" placeholder="누수 위치 및 발생 사유"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="body-text">
    본인이 관리 또는 소유하고 있는 건물 내에 상수도 누수가 발생하여 「제주특별자치도 수도급수 조례」
    제39조 및 같은 조례 시행규칙 제28조제3항에 따라 위와 같이 신청합니다.
  </div>

  <div class="sign-date" id="sign_date_display"></div>
  <div class="sign-input-row">
    신청인 :&nbsp;<input class="fi-inline" id="applicant_name" oninput="syncName()" placeholder="성명">&nbsp;(인)
  </div>
  <div class="sign-input-row">
    (수용가와의 관계 :&nbsp;<input class="fi-inline" id="relation" placeholder="관계" style="width:90px;">&nbsp;)
  </div>
  <div class="recipient-line">제주특별자치도지사 귀하</div>
  <div class="attach-text">
    붙임 : 1. 누수수리확인서 또는 영수증<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. 누수수리공사 사진
  </div>

  <div class="cut-wrap"><hr class="cut-line"><span class="cut-label">접수증</span><hr class="cut-line"></div>
  <div class="receipt-title">옥내 누수사용료 적용 신청서 접수증</div>
  <div class="receipt-row">접 수 번 호 :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;수용가번호 :</div>
  <div class="receipt-row">소유자(관리자) :</div>
  <p class="receipt-confirm">귀하께서 신청하신 옥내누수사용료 적용신청서가 접수되었음을 확인합니다.</p>
  <div class="receipt-sign">년&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;월&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;일<br>접수담당자&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(인)</div>
  <div class="note-box">
    ※ 1. 옥내누수 현장확인 및 누수량을 선정한 연후에 조정된 고지서를 재발급합니다.<br>
    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2. 현장 확인하여 수용가 부주의로 인한 물탱크 및 변기 볼탑과 노출관의 누수는 감면대상에서 제외됩니다.
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ PAGE 2 ═══ -->
<div class="page">
  <div class="page-title">옥내누수(업체위탁 · 자체수리) 수리확인서</div>

  <div class="field-rows">
    <!-- · 기호 고정, 나머지 글자 space-between -->
    <div class="fr">
      <div class="fl">·<span class="fl-inner"><span>주</span><span>소</span></span></div>
      <div class="fv"><span class="fi-sync" id="s_addr"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fr">
      <div class="fl">·<span class="fl-inner"><span>수</span><span>용</span><span>가</span><span>성</span><span>명</span></span></div>
      <div class="fv"><span class="fi-sync" id="s_custname"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fr">
      <div class="fl">·<span class="fl-inner"><span>수</span><span>용</span><span>가</span><span>번</span><span>호</span></span></div>
      <div class="fv"><span class="fi-sync" id="s_custno"></span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="fr">
      <div class="fl">·<span class="fl-inner"><span>누</span><span>수</span><span>위</span><span>치</span></span></div>
      <div class="fv" style="white-space:pre-wrap; line-height:1.5; align-items:flex-start; padding-top:5px; min-height:28px;">
        <span class="fi-sync" id="s_leak_loc"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fr">
      <div class="fl">·<span class="fl-inner"><span>수</span><span>리</span><span>일</span><span>시</span></span></div>
      <div class="fv"><span class="fi-sync" id="s_repair_date"></span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="company-box">
    <div class="cr">
      <div class="cl"><span style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;width:100%;"><span>상</span><span>호</span></span></div>
      <div class="cv"><input class="fi" id="biz_sangho" placeholder="상호명" value="찰떡누수"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cr">
      <div class="cl"><span style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;width:100%;"><span>사</span><span>업</span><span>자</span><span>등</span><span>록</span><span>번</span><span>호</span></span></div>
      <div class="cv"><input class="fi" id="biz_reg" placeholder="000-00-00000" value="617-64-00891"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cr">
      <div class="cl"><span style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;width:100%;">
        <span>(대</span><span>표</span><span>자)</span><span>성명</span>
      </span></div>
<div class="cv" style="position:relative; overflow:visible; justify-content:flex-start;">
        <input class="fi" id="biz_ceo" placeholder="대표자 성명" style="flex:none; width:35px;" value="윤승환">
        <!-- (인) + 도장이 세로로 쌓임: 도장이 위, (인) 텍스트가 아래 -->
        <div style="position:relative; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; margin-left:10px; min-width:40px;">
          <!-- 도장: (인) 위치 위에 absolute로 겹침 -->
          <img id="stamp_img"
            style="display:none; position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%, -50%);
       width:36px; height:36px; object-fit:contain; opacity:0.9; z-index:10; pointer-events:none;">
          <span style="font-size:8.5pt; white-space:nowrap;">(인)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cr">
      <div class="cl"><span style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;width:100%;">
        <span>(사</span><span>업</span><span>장)</span><span>주소</span>
      </span></div>
      <div class="cv"><input class="fi" id="biz_addr" placeholder="사업장 주소" value="제주도 제주시 애월읍 애월로 165"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cr">
      <div class="cl"><span style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;width:100%;"><span>전</span><span>화</span></span></div>
      <div class="cv"><input class="fi" id="biz_tel" placeholder="전화번호" value="010-5183-8757"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="note-small">※ 사업자등록이 안되어 있는 개인(업체)이 수리하였을 때는 부품 구매 영수증을 첨부해야함.</div>
  <div class="photo-note">사 진 대 장&nbsp;&nbsp;수리전·후 사진 첨부</div>
  <div class="confirm-footer">
    위와 같이 옥내 누수를 수리하였음을 확인합니다.<br>
    <span id="confirm_date_display"></span><br>
    <strong>제주특별자치도지사 귀하</strong>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 사진대장 4장 -->
<div class="photo-page-4" id="photo4page">
  <div class="photo-page-title">사진대장</div>
  <div class="photo-grid-4">
    <div class="photo-card"><div class="photo-header">배관 노출 및 누수점 확인</div><div class="photo-area"><div class="photo-upload-area" onclick="triggerUpload('inp1')"><input type="file" accept="image/*" id="inp1" style="display:none;"><img id="img1" style="display:none;"><span class="photo-placeholder" id="ph1">클릭하여 사진 추가</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="photo-card"><div class="photo-header">누수 부위 배관 절단</div><div class="photo-area"><div class="photo-upload-area" onclick="triggerUpload('inp2')"><input type="file" accept="image/*" id="inp2" style="display:none;"><img id="img2" style="display:none;"><span class="photo-placeholder" id="ph2">클릭하여 사진 추가</span></div></div></div>
    <div class="photo-card"><div class="photo-header">배관 수리 및 교체 완료</div><div class="photo-area"><div class="photo-upload-area" onclick="triggerUpload('inp3')"><input type="file" accept="image/*" id="inp3" style="display:none;"><img id="img3" style="display:none;"><span class="photo-placeholder" id="ph3">클릭하여 사진 추가</span></div></div></div>
